<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" media="screen and (max-width:768px)" href="css/mobile.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/logoDeltha.ico">
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-4bw+/aepP/YC94hEpVNVgiZdgIC5+VKNBQNGCHeKRQN+PtmoHDEXuppvnDJzQIu9" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-HwwvtgBNo3bZJJLYd8oVXjrBZt8cqVSpeBNS5n7C8IVInixGAoxmnlMuBnhbgrkm"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- Link CSS JS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/generalStyles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/financiacion.css">
    <title>Deltha Car´s</title>

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Teko&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Jquery -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    
    <%- include('./shared/nav.ejs') %>

    <section>
        <div class="container-fluid header-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <div class="header-content-container">
                <div class="title-container">
                    <h1>
                        FINANCIACIÓN
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <div class="description-header">
                    <p class="text-center header-description">
                        Si necesitas financiación consúltanos, lo hacemos de una manera rápida y sencilla con unas
                        tarifas muy
                        competitivas adaptándonos siempre a tus necesidades
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="trian"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pasos -->
    <section>
        <div class="big-info-car-container container-fluid d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
            <div class="pixel-adjust">
                <div class="title-section container text-center">
                    <h2 class="info-title">
                        En 3 Sencillos Pasos
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="container-steps mt-5">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="step col-12 col-md-4">
                            <div class="icon text-center">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="60" height="60" fill="red"
                                    class="bi bi-calculator" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                    <path
                                        d="M12 1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v12a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V2a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h8zM4 0a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4z" />
                                    <path
                                        d="M4 2.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h7a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v2a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-7a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-2zm0 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1zm0 3a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1zm0 3a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1zm3-6a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1zm0 3a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1zm0 3a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1zm3-6a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1zm0 3a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v4a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-4z" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-title text-center mt-4">
                                <h2 class="steps-tilte">
                                    Calculamos la financiación
                                </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-info ">
                                <p class="text-center step-description">
                                    Calculamos la financiación que necesitas con entidades de reconocido prestigio.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step col-12 col-md-4">
                            <div class="icon text-center">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="60" height="60" fill="red"
                                    class="bi bi-pencil-square" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                    <path
                                        d="M15.502 1.94a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .706L14.459 3.69l-2-2L13.502.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .707 0l1.293 1.293zm-1.75 2.456-2-2L4.939 9.21a.5.5 0 0 0-.121.196l-.805 2.414a.25.25 0 0 0 .316.316l2.414-.805a.5.5 0 0 0 .196-.12l6.813-6.814z" />
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                                        d="M1 13.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2.5 15h11a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-6a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0v6a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-11a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-11a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5H9a.5.5 0 0 0 0-1H2.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1 2.5v11z" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-title text-center mt-4">
                                <h2 class="steps-tilte">
                                    Aplicamos el resultado
                                </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-info ">
                                <p class="text-center step-description">
                                    Aplicamos la financiación a la medida de tus necesidades.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step col-12 col-md-4">
                            <div class="icon text-center">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="60" height="60" fill="red"
                                    class="bi bi-check-circle" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                    <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z" />
                                    <path
                                        d="M10.97 4.97a.235.235 0 0 0-.02.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-1.071-1.05z" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-title text-center mt-4">
                                <h2 class="steps-tilte">
                                    Aprobado!
                                </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-info ">
                                <p class="text-center step-description">
                                    Una vez aprobado nos hacemos cargo de todo lo demás.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <!-- Coche de ocacion -->
    <section class="container-fluid">
        <div class="oca-container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
            <div class="back-color">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="question-container col-12 col-md-7 mt-5 text-center">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="oca-title ">¿Quieres comprar un coche de ocasión?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="">
                                Busca en nuestro Stock el coche que más se ajuste a tus necesidades. Si no lo encuentras, no te
                                preocupes, nosotros lo buscaremos por ti.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="btn-holder col-12 col-md-4 mb-2 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <button class="btn btn-danger btn-stock">
                            <a class="link" href="/stock">VER STOCK
                            </a>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./shared/footer.ejs') %>

</body>